title: Ep. #60 | Catching Up: Young K
description:
Young K joins Eric to discuss his pre-Day6 trainee days, new album The Book of Us: The Demon, and thoughts on being in a band in the South Korean music industry.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
